{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6855ab4e30","title":"掉友人易咏啡","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1f50f09d05","index":0,"year":1915,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"6855ab4e30"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji1","name":"毛泽东全集第1卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a8ed554bc0","type":"paragraph","text":"掉友人易咏啡","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"6855ab4e30"},{"id":"c2d0ccaf71","type":"paragraph","text":"（1915年5月）胡房多反复，千里度龙山，程移待游，独令我来何济世；生死安足论，百年会有役（没》，奇花初苗，特因君去尚非时。[1]这是毛评东为惊念同学易殊味所写的规联。易咏硅，即易品陶，潮商衡山人。湖南省立第一师范学校第八班学生，于1915年3月病齿家中。由校长张于、学监王季范、教员杨昌济发起，学校于5月23日召开了进算会。师生共送换诗晚联256首（副），并编印成册，题为《易君味雅追牌录》。诗联内容多合“停念学友，寻忘国耻”之意。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"6855ab4e30"}],"page":{"id":"f0b87e0db8","publicationId":"maoquanji1","articleId":"6855ab4e30","start":172,"end":172}}}},"__N_SSG":true}